Bid Manager
Al Fursan Recruitment
Location:
Abu Dhabi
Date: 01-05-2014
Payrate: 10,000 To 10,000 Monthly (AED)
Job Type: Employee
Job Status: Full Time
Categories:
IT
Managerial
Al Fursan Recruitment
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
The Bid Manager has the following responsibilities:
Ensure efficient use of Company resources to deliver: • Timely and effective responses to Requests for Information (RFI) and Requests for Proposal (RFP) are delivered that meet Customer requirements and company targets.
• Deliver a continuous and high level of Customer satisfaction.
To assist in identifying and evaluating new TETRA business opportunities, and in defining and implementing policy and future strategy.
Continuous, high level of quality internal and external management reporting.
Planning and managing the bid
Support the tender design process to ensure delivery is on-time
Be able to develop innovative and creative solutions and specifications
Manage and develop relationships with existing and potential suppliers.
Produce management reports to highlight the progress on each bid
Making sure the commercial proposal is consistent with the technical solution
Manage bid administration and resources
